Suggests: tokenshield-unified
Description: TokenShield command-line interface
 TokenShield is a PCI compliance gateway demonstrating credit card
 tokenization using modern proxy technologies. This package provides
 the command-line interface for managing the TokenShield system.
 .
 Features include:
  - Token management (list, search, revoke)
  - API key operations (create, list, revoke)
  - Activity monitoring
  - Statistics viewing
  - Configuration file support
  - Cross-platform compatibility